data.description: Welcome to Woodmere! This patio home sits on a very large corner lot and features 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. Inside, enjoy granite countertops and stainless steel appliances in the kitchen, vaulted ceilings and a fireplace in the great room, and ample sized guest bedrooms. The master suite features an en suite bath and tile flooring. This home offers easy access to I-85 and sits on a large corner lot with a fenced backyard and screened porch. A detached storage shed remains with the home. Don't miss out - schedule a showing today! 2024-04-22
